<h2>Blockquote</h2>

<blockquote>
  <p>Blockquote is set to have a left border, with the browser default padding removed.
A <code>cite</code> will be right aligned and italicized.</p>
</blockquote>

<div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nt">&lt;blockquote&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>Keep it secret. Keep it safe.<span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;cite&gt;</span>Gandalf the Gray<span class="nt">&lt;/cite&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/blockquote&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
